{"tid":550886,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國核態勢報告建議擴大核武能力　視中俄為主要威脅","createTime":"2018-02-05T07:16:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T09:42:55.000Z","uid":60545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"56d02861d85e5b819155d989720cdbc0e640528d","tid":550886,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T07:16:49.000Z","msg":"美國國防部發表《核態勢報告》，將中國、俄羅斯及北韓視為主要核威脅，但會繼續堅持在極端情況下才使用核武的立場，建議美國擴大核武能力，發展低威力核武應對俄羅斯威脅，提高威懾力。<br />\n<br />\n報告表示，一旦美國或盟友受到常規武器攻擊，只會在極端情況下才考慮使用核武。有專家批評，美國的做法會令美俄錯估形勢的風險增加。<br />\n<br />\n美國副國務卿香農表示，莫斯科留有大量非戰略核武器，繼續對非戰略核武器和戰略系統進行現代化；中國亦進行核力量現代化和擴張，批評中俄正在挑戰自由和開放的國際秩序。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1379025-20180203.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1379025-20180203.htm&d=XukUKqYru8qynqQlz644MJnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=2d81109d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1379025-20180203.htm&h=c01ccec2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1379025-20180203.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1e23aea3767cc8583f1409159e0dfbe38ca89c4a","tid":550886,"uid":4783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T07:38:57.000Z","msg":"發展低威力核武<br />\n<br />\n即係講緊常規作戰都有機會用核武，開始用冷戰思維對待中俄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618591cfd8d8b0223a6a68b4e115bf51b589e5bd","tid":550886,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:36:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"086437e2ff597c810c1e280d9d53b7716bb4d232","tid":550886,"uid":84128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T09:42:55.000Z","msg":"Fallout<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}